data.title: Congratulatory messages
data.meta_description: Prime Minister Lawrence Gonzi has received messages of congratulations on his appointment from Belarus Prime Minister Sergei Sidorsky, European Commissioner for Enlargement Gunter Verheugen, and from Australian Prime Minister John Howard.
data.text: Prime Minister Lawrence Gonzi has received messages of congratulations on his appointment from Belarus Prime Minister Sergei Sidorsky, European Commissioner for Enlargement Gunter Verheugen, and from Australian Prime Minister John Howard.
